RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT B.CONTRACT_REF_NO , B.USER_REF_NO , B.CUSTOM_REF_NO , B.PRODUCT_CODE , B.COUNTERPARTY, B.CONTRACT_CCY , C.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION , E.CUSTOMER_NAME1 , F.CCY_NAME FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT B ,OLTMS_PRODUCT C,OLTMS_CUSTOMER E, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN F WHERE C.PRODUCT_CODE =B.PRODUCT_CODE AND E.CUSTOMER_NO = B.COUNTERPARTY AND F.CCY_CODE = B.CONTRACT_CCY AND B.CONTRACT_REF_NO IN (SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_REVISION_SCH)
